<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>A Kuolna Gankuong</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Zie zan hun thiptak a chun,
 Phalbi vuk dai chim nuoiah;
 Bethlehem bawng In tawmah,
 Lal Krista A hung pieng tai;
 Van mipi'n a hung thau hi,
 I gitloh tan di'n;
 Lei leh van Lal himaleh,(2)
 Sambang a zalna gan kuong ahi.

[V2]
 2. Silhpuon nemin a tuom ui,
 Gan kuongah A lu a ngai;
 Gimthei taka hung piengin,
 A nu Mari lunggil chu;
 Chemzamin a sun let tai,
 Pa cha khat neih sun;
 Gitlote dinga hung chu(2)
 David khawpi ah A hung pieng tai.

[V3]
 3. Angelte'n khuta dawmin,
 Zah takin a chibai ui;
 Zie zan thawmhauh um taka,
 A lungakna mun tawm chu
 Lalpa lopina'n a salh,
 Belampute leh
 Michingten a chibai ui(2)
 Sambang zalna bawng In tawm nuoiah.

[V4]
 4. Ei un le Amah lawpin,
 Bethlehem lam zuon hitiu;
 Van mi thiengte gen guol khan,
 Nausen puona tuom ngei chu;
 Gan kuongah va mu leu hing,
 Chun, a kienga chun,
 Nitum zankhuo - nuom hitiu,(2)
 Sambang zalna gan In tawm nuoiah.</lyrics>
<author>Upa Rokunga</author>
<hymn_number>17</hymn_number>
</song>